history.content: It will be slightly helpful to take EE 126 before CS 189, but not by much (I did 189 before 126 and there was maybe 1-2 hours worth of reading up on probability to do), so there is a small but not particularly significant advantage. More important is mathematical maturity (which you would practice in EE 126). You could take both concurrently, as well.
